ActNational Capital Act
SubjectLease with Kruger Products L.P. - ** NCC **
PrecisOrder Authorizing the NATIONAL CAPITAL COMMISSION to ENTER INTO a lease with KRUGER PRODUCTS L.P. for an initial term of five years, beginning on March 28, 2028, and grant four extension options of five years each, beginning on March 28, 2033, March 28, 2038, March 28, 2043, and March 28, 2048, to occupy part of the premises located at 20 LAURIER STREET, in Gatineau, Quebec,
